title.rendered: N95 Respirator & Surgical mask (Level 3) Cupped- PB005, Box of 20

content.rendered:
N95 Respirator & Surgical mask (Level 3) Cupped- PB005

The Strapit PB005 Healthcare Respirator and Surgical Mask is designed to provide respiratory protection to the user from certain airborne particles. The PB005 Particulate Respirator and Surgical Mask, when fitted correctly, protects healthcare works from harmful airborne particles around 0.3 microns or smaller which includes fine dust aerosols and also viruses.

This protection is 98% of airborne particles < 0.3 microns

excerpt.rendered:
• FFP3/N95 Certified as a Particular Respirator
  • Meets European EN149 Standard which closely conforms to the P2 Standard
  • Meets TGA Standard as a Respirator and Surgical Mask
  • Bacterial Filtration Efficiency (BFE) >99% according to ASTM F2101
  • Fluid Resistance 160mmHg according to ASTM F1862 (Level 3 surgical mask)
  • Metal Nose Clip for flexible face fit and seal
  • 4 Ply with adjustable head bands
  • No Latex
